      • Collaborator

        public Collaborator(java.lang.String id,
                    java.lang.String fullName,
                    java.lang.String email,
                    java.lang.String extension)
        Constructs a new general Collaborator object with the provided ID, full name, email, and extension. This constructor initializes the Collaborator object with the provided information.

        Preconditions:

        • The id, fullName, email, and extension parameters must be Strings.

        Postconditions:

        • A new general Collaborator object is created with the provided ID, full name, email, and extension (optional).
        Parameters:
        id - The ID of the collaborator.
        fullName - The full name of the collaborator.
        email - The email address of the collaborator.
        extension - The extension number of the collaborator (optional).
